headline: Morgan Stanley Maintained an Overweight Rating on AbbVie (ABBV)
summary: AbbVie Inc. (NYSE:ABBV) is one of the best high growth stocks. On June 30, Morgan Stanley maintained an Overweight rating and a $250 price target on AbbVie, in light of the company’s recent acquisition announcement.
